0:["nHUYCTVjsWTesso99Tkid",[[["",{"children":["docs",{"children":["platforms",{"children":["__PAGE__",{}]}]}]},"$undefined","$undefined",true],["",{"children":["docs",{"children":["platforms",{"children":["__PAGE__",{},[["$L1",["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h1",null,{"children":"Platform Mappings"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After computing the receiver profile, the SDK maps each primitive to platform-specific parameters. All mappings are deterministic and config-driven."}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"Temperature (from SG)"}],["$","p",null,{"children":["Temperature maps ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"inversely"}]," to Signal Gain. A high-gain receiver discriminates sharply between signals — in LLMs that means low temperature (crisp, deterministic outputs). A low-gain receiver is broadly receptive — that means higher temperature (exploratory outputs)."]}],["$","pre",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"children":"temperature = t_max - (SG / 100) × (t_max - t_min)\n\n# Anthropic range [0.0, 1.0]:  SG=80 → temp=0.20, SG=20 → temp=0.80\n# OpenAI range    [0.0, 2.0]:  SG=80 → temp=0.40, SG=20 → temp=1.60"}]}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"Max tokens (from TI)"}],["$","p",null,{"children":["Temporal Integration maps ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"directly"}]," to max_tokens. Long integration needs more room to reason over more context."]}],["$","pre",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"children":"max_tokens = t_min + (TI / 100) × (t_max - t_min), rounded to nearest 256\n\n# Anthropic range [256, 8192]: TI=10 → 1024, TI=77 → 6400"}]}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"Context strategy (from TI)"}],["$","pre",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"children":"TI ≥ 65 → long_window       (pass full context)\nTI ≥ 35 → rolling_summary   (summarize old turns, keep recent full)\nTI < 35 → frequent_grounding (re-inject key facts each turn)"}]}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"Tool use strategy (from AR + FT)"}],["$","pre",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"children":"FT ≥ 65 → explicit_confirmation  (verify before every tool call)\nAR ≤ 35 → cautious_chaining      (chain tools conservatively)\nAR ≥ 65 → aggressive             (act decisively)\nelse    → fail_fast              (attempt + retry on failure)"}]}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"Retry strategy (from UE)"}],["$","pre",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"children":"UE ≥ 65 → aggressive   (retry on any non-success)\nUE ≥ 35 → moderate     (retry on transient errors)\nUE < 35 → minimal      (retry only on network errors)"}]}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"Model selection (from TI + SG + UE)"}],["$","pre",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"children":"TI ≥ 65 and SG ≤ 40 → complex_reasoning model\nTI ≤ 30 and UE ≥ 65 → speed_priority model\nelse                  → default model"}]}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"Platform configs"}],["$","h3",null,{"children":"Anthropic"}],["$","pre",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"children":"temperature_range: [0.0, 1.0]\nmax_tokens_range:  [256, 8192]\nmodels:\n  default:           claude-sonnet-4-6\n  complex_reasoning: claude-opus-4-6\n  speed_priority:    claude-sonnet-4-6\n  cheap_high_volume: claude-haiku-4-5-20251001"}]}],["$","h3",null,{"children":"OpenAI"}],["$","pre",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"children":"temperature_range: [0.0, 2.0]\nmax_tokens_range:  [256, 16384]\nmodels:\n  default:           gpt-4o\n  complex_reasoning: o1\n  speed_priority:    gpt-4o-mini"}]}],["$","h3",null,{"children":"Open source"}],["$","pre",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"children":"temperature_range: [0.0, 2.0]\nmax_tokens_range:  [256, 8192]\nmodels:\n  default:           llama-3-70b\n  complex_reasoning: deepseek-r1\n  speed_priority:    llama-3-8b"}]}],["$","h3",null,{"children":"Generic"}],["$","pre",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"children":"temperature_range: [0.0, 1.0]\nmax_tokens_range:  [256, 4096]\nmodel_recommendation: null  (platform-neutral)"}]}]]}],null],null],null]},[null,["$","$L2",null,{"parallelRouterKey":"children","segmentPath":["ch